Package com.icesoft.faces.async.render

Interface Summary
AsyncRenderer  
Renderable The Renderable interface represents the PersistentFacesState of a managed bean to the rest of the classes in the Rendering API.
 

Class Summary
DelayRenderer The DelayRenderer is type of GroupAsyncRenderer that is used to request a single render pass on a group of Renderables.
GroupAsyncRenderer The GroupAsyncRenderer is the foundation class for other types of renderers that are designed to operate on a group of Renderables.
IntervalRenderer The IntervalRenderer is type of GroupAsyncRenderer that is used to request a single render pass on a group of Renderables.
OnDemandRenderer The OnDemandRenderer is type of GroupAsyncRenderer that is used to request a render pass on a group of Renderables.
RenderManager The RenderManager is the central class for developers wanting to do server-initiated rendering.
